 apply","items":[{"text":"Site","shouldBeSelected":false},{"text":"Call date","shouldBeSelected":false},{"text":"Name","shouldBeSelected":true},{"text":"Sex","shouldBeSelected":true},{"text":"Date of birth","shouldBeSelected":true},{"text":"Address","shouldBeSelected":true},{"text":"Postcode","shouldBeSelected":true},{"text":"Profession","shouldBeSelected":false},{"text":"Severity","shouldBeSelected":false}],"feedback":{"correct":"<p><strong>That's right!</strong></p><p>Personal data refers to information relating to an identified or identifiable natural person. For this data set that means: name, sex, date of birth, address and postcode.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>","incorrect":"<p><strong>Are you sure about that?</strong></p><p>Personal data refers to information relating to an identified or identifiable natural person. For this data set that means: name, sex, date of birth, address and postcode.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"}}}]},{"block":{"title":"What is the risk level of each data point?","type":"Title"},"components":[{"properties":{"instruction":"Choose one option then select Submit.","items":[{"text":"Site","options":[{"text":"low","isCorrect":true},{"text":"medium","isCorrect":false},{"text":"high","isCorrect":false}]},{"text":"Call date","options":[{"text":"low","isCorrect":true},{"text":"medium","isCorrect":false},{"text":"high","isCorrect":false}]},{"text":"Name","options":[{"text":"low","isCorrect":false},{"text":"medium","isCorrect":false},{"text":"high","isCorrect":true}]},{"text":"Sex","options":[{"text":"low","isCorrect":false},{"text":"medium","isCorrect":true},{"text":"high","isCorrect":false}]},{"text":"Date of birth","options":[{"text":"low","isCorrect":false},{"text":"medium","isCorrect":true},{"text":"high","isCorrect":false}]},{"text":"Address","options":[{"text":"low","isCorrect":false},{"text":"medium","isCorrect":false},{"text":"high","isCorrect":true}]},{"text":"Postcode","options":[{"text":"low","isCorrect":false},{"text":"medium","isCorrect":true},{"text":"hi